            Events Store
          </span>
        </div>

        {/* Title */}
        <div className="mb-10">
          <h1 className="text-3xl font-bold text-[#1a1a1a] mb-2">
            Create your events store
          </h1>
          <p className="text-[#888888]">
            Set up your event ticketing platform in just a few steps.
